column2: Warning: Your charge level has increased.
Shadowstep to your target and deliver a dazing strike. Gain superspeed if you interrupt an enemy.
Double-click to apply this appearance to your current boots. This will unlock the skin in your wardrobe.
Smack your foe with a metal bar. It has a chance to break.
Strike an enemy and draw water from them, causing them to deliver a healing burst to your allies.

Double-click to apply this look to any other staff. This will also unlock this skin for your wardrobe.
<c=@flavor>It is said that this staff was carried by Heleyne, one of the Envoys that served as shepherds of souls into the Mists.</c>
Find the sensors in the second location.
<c=@abilitytype>Dual Attack.</c> Unleash a volley of ice and earth at your enemies.
Used in the Mystic Forge to create legendary weapons.
Win the favor of the circus
You took gold place in this race!
<c=@flavor>This elegant scepter was the most desired weapon amongst mesmers of the past.</c>
Unlocks the recipe to craft For Science.
